  "instructions": [
    "1. Heat oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "2. Add chopped onion and sauté until softened.",
    "3. Add sliced beef and cook until browned.",
    "4. Add ground spices (cumin, coriander, turmeric, garam masala) and cook for 1 minute.",
    "5. Add chopped red chili and cook for another minute.",
    "6. Add water and bring to a boil.",
    "7. Reduce heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "8. Serve with fluffy basmati rice and british naan bread.",
    "9. Garnish with chopped cilantro, if desired."
